<paragraph pageId="3" pageNumber="10">Material examined.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="3" pageNumber="10">Mississippi, Vicksburg; in decaying leaves and twigs, October 2, H.E. Ewing, coll.; Lectotype, designated by J.T. Salmon, 1958; original US National Museum of Natural History catalog number 42981; current catalog number 9026.</paragraph>
